{"_path":"/maps/_ai/mechanistic-interpretability","_dir":"_ai","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"机制可解释性 (Mechanistic Interpretability)","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"机制可解释性-mechanistic-interpretability"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"机制可解释性 (Mechanistic Interpretability)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"transformerlens逆向工程-gpt-风格模型的标准工具"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TransformerLens：逆向工程 GPT 风格模型的标准工具"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TransformerLens 由 Neel Nanda 开发，是机制可解释性领域的事实标准工具。它提供对 GPT 风格语言模型内部的深度访问能力，包括激活缓存、注意力模式分析、因果追踪和激活修补（Activation Patching）。使用它可以重现经典研究：归纳头（Induction Heads）负责 few-shot 学习的注意力回路、间接对象识别（IOI）解析代词指代消解的电路、以及定位执行简单数学运算的子网络。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/TransformerLensOrg/TransformerLens","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TransformerLens GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://neelnanda-io.github.io/TransformerLens/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TransformerLens 教程"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arxiv.org/html/2404.15255v1","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Activation Patching 论文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"稀疏自动编码器将神经元分解为可解释特征"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"稀疏自动编码器：将神经元分解为可解释特征"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"稀疏自动编码器（SAE）是当前可解释性研究的热点方向。它将高维激活向量分解为稀疏的、可解释的\"特征\"基向量，这些特征往往对应人类可理解的概念：数字、颜色、语法结构、甚至抽象的情感概念。Anthropic 在 Claude 3 Sonnet 上的研究发现，约 70% 的 SAE 特征可被人类解释，实现了从\"多义神经元\"到\"单语义特征\"的突破。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://transformer-circuits.pub/2024/scaling-monosemanticity/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Anthropic SAE 研究"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://nickjiang.substack.com/p/a-primer-on-sparse-autoencoders","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SAE 入门指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/jbloomAus/SAELens","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SAELens GitHub"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"nnsight-与-ndif远程可解释性实验基础设施"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"nnsight 与 NDIF：远程可解释性实验基础设施"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"传统可解释性工具受限于单机 GPU 显存，难以分析 70B+ 参数模型。nnsight 通过远程执行架构解决了这个问题——本地编写干预逻辑，远程在大型 GPU 集群执行，只返回分析结果。National Deep Inference Facility (NDIF) 为研究者提供免费的远程可解释性计算资源，让任何研究者都能分析 Llama-2-70B 级别的模型。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://nnsight.net/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"nnsight 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/ndif-team/nnsight","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"nnsight GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ndif.us/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"NDIF 官网"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"归纳头few-shot-学习的注意力回路"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"归纳头：Few-shot 学习的注意力回路"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"归纳头是 Transformer 中一种特殊的注意力头模式，负责识别序列中的重复模式并进行 few-shot 学习。当一个 token 在序列中重复出现时，归纳头能够\"复制\"之前出现的模式，这是大模型上下文学习能力的重要机制。通过 TransformerLens 的激活修补技术，可以精确定位这些回路并研究其工作机制。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://aclanthology.org/2025.acl-long.442.pdf","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Circuit Stability 论文"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.alignmentforum.org/posts/jP9KDyMkchuv6tHwm/how-to-become-a-mechanistic-interpretability-researcher","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何成为可解释性研究员"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"表征工程主动修改模型内部行为"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"表征工程：主动修改模型内部行为"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"表征工程（Representation Engineering）是通过定位和修改模型内部表征来实现特定行为的技术。包括增强诚实性（检测并抑制模型幻觉）、提升有用性（增强指令遵循能力）、以及改善安全性（抑制有害输出）。这为 AI 对齐提供了一条不同于 RLHF 的技术路径——直接操作模型的内部表征而非仅仅调整输出分布。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.anthropic.com/research/transformer-circuits","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Anthropic 可解释性研究"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arena-chapter1-transformer-interp.streamlit.app/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ARENA 可解释性教程"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"transformerlens逆向工程-gpt-风格模型的标准工具","depth":2,"text":"TransformerLens：逆向工程 GPT 风格模型的标准工具"},{"id":"稀疏自动编码器将神经元分解为可解释特征","depth":2,"text":"稀疏自动编码器：将神经元分解为可解释特征"},{"id":"nnsight-与-ndif远程可解释性实验基础设施","depth":2,"text":"nnsight 与 NDIF：远程可解释性实验基础设施"},{"id":"归纳头few-shot-学习的注意力回路","depth":2,"text":"归纳头：Few-shot 学习的注意力回路"},{"id":"表征工程主动修改模型内部行为","depth":2,"text":"表征工程：主动修改模型内部行为"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:mechanistic-interpretability.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/mechanistic-interpretability.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/mechanistic-interpretability","_extension":"md"}